python-twitter-examples
------------------------------------------------------------------------

A set of Python scripts to demonstrate interactions with the Twitter API
via the Python Twitter Tools module:

	http://mike.verdone.ca/twitter/

This collection was developed for a laboratory in social data mining
for the Digital Sociology, Digital Journalism and Creating Social Media
MA courses at the Centre for Creative and Social Technology, Goldsmiths,
University of London:

	http://castlondon.com/

For comments, updates and patch submissions, please contact:

	Daniel Jones <d.jones@gold.ac.uk>
	http://www.erase.net

------------------------------------------------------------------------
